topic.title: Fact checker checkers
topic.body: Just curious, has anyone come across a check/balance to fact checkers on clearnet? ie regular people who fact check the so-called "fact-checkers"

1604114604_19RBy1R77se3kYGB4ZLXCVowdKrcq.body:
> [claude](#comment_37_1MUCEEtbLUYFpc6vqhp4F5u4ia8MJ9RGK1): 

> [joeandblow](#comment_3_1N2VV3mbu9KLbSxTpedj9JvaQ51v9vNEN3): Uhh, are you even seeding the zite? It has 8 peers, but nobody has any data yet.

I didn't realize at 1st... should be good now. I just accessed it from a seperate computer.

1605282602_16NS3rBdW9zpLmLSQoD8nLTtNVsRF.body: Countless dystopia movies show us the ultimate outcome of AI, but we still don't acknowledge the dangers. It's not even sci-fi anymore. Technology is evolving at a faster rate than we are unfortunately.
